    <simplesect>

<para>INTERFACE: This interface holds the implementation for the <link linkend="dd/d5a/a00538">ScreenManager</link> which is responsible for loading the content in each screen and displaying each screen. The <link linkend="dd/d5a/a00538">ScreenManager</link> contains a stack of screens which allows for multiple screens to be prepared for loading whilst only one is an active screen </para>
    </simplesect>
